{"type": "article", "id": 13054, "title": "视觉障碍患者专用智能手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-05T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125741VkQl8jFxLa5XBwJg.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，韩国设计设计公司 Dot 推出了一款专门为视觉障碍患者设计的智能手表，除了普通的智能手表拥有的定位，导航，信息等功能之外，它拥有 24 个点，这些点能够上下浮动，速率最高为每秒100 次，一次可创建 4 个或者 1 个盲文字符。通过这些点，视觉障碍患者能够获取大量信息，并且可以系统地学习盲文。Dot 还有圆形表盘设计，含有 18 个点。Dot 现在正在融资，产品预计今年 12 月正式面市，售价约 300 美元（约合人民币 1860 元）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140715g3j8iwouVAGIspl6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41809291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140715gSawNcRpqUTY6PrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.11246944\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407165SiBDImpxbVewnUK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140716wvJxyVtihQKLEduM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140717cL42agKJiP6OrTbf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75183374\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140717m9UcS0dRv8bqBaDl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140717I76E0pKc2HXtZDQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}